com.pb.sawdust.tabledata.transform.row

Interface ContextDataRow<C>

  • Type Parameters:
    C - The type of the context held by this data row.
    All Superinterfaces:
    DataRow
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DegenerateContextDataRow

    public interface ContextDataRow<C>
extends DataRow
    The ContextDataRow is a data row associated with a particular "context." Basically, this interface allows a data row to be a simple container holding some informational object which can be accessed.
